260
0:10:43.26,000 --> 0:10:45,000
Now there's a big "if," of course,

261
0:10:45.26,000 --> 0:10:48,000
and it is if insects produce meat

262
0:10:48.26,000 --> 0:10:5,000
that is of good quality.

263
0:10:50.26,000 --> 0:10:52,000
Well there have been all kinds of analyses

264
0:10:52.26,000 --> 0:10:55,000
and in terms of protein, or fat, or vitamins,

265
0:10:55.26,000 --> 0:10:57,000
it's very good.

266
0:10:57.26,000 --> 0:10:59,000
In fact, it's comparable

267
0:10:59.26,000 --> 0:11:01,000
to anything we eat as meat at the moment.

268
0:11:01.26,000 --> 0:11:03,000
And even in terms of calories, it is very good.

269
0:11:03.26,000 --> 0:11:05,000
