270
0:11:05.26,000 --> 0:11:07,000
has the same amount of calories

271
0:11:07.26,000 --> 0:11:09,000
as 10 hot dogs, or six Big Macs.

272
0:11:09.26,000 --> 0:11:11,000
So that's four points for insects.

273
0:11:11.26,000 --> 0:11:14,000
(Laughter)

274
0:11:14.26,000 --> 0:11:16,000
I can go on,

275
0:11:16.26,000 --> 0:11:18,000
and I could make many more points for insects,

276
0:11:18.26,000 --> 0:11:2,000
but time doesn't allow this.

277
0:11:20.26,000 --> 0:11:22,000
So the question is, why not eat insects?

278
0:11:22.26,000 --> 0:11:24,000
I gave you at least four arguments in favor.

279
0:11:24.26,000 --> 0:11:26,000
We'll have to.

280
0:11:26.26,000 --> 0:11:28,000
Even if you don't like it,

281
0:11:28.26,000 --> 0:11:3,000
you'll have to get used to this

282
0:11:30.26,000 --> 0:11:32,000
because at the moment,

283
0:11:32.26,000 --> 0:11:34,000
70 percent of all our agricultural land

284
0:11:34.26,000 --> 0:11:36,000
is being used to produce livestock.

285
0:11:36.26,000 --> 0:11:38,000
That's not only the land

286
0:11:38.26,000 --> 0:11:4,000
where the livestock is walking and feeding,

287
0:11:40.26,000 --> 0:11:42,000
but it's also other areas

288
0:11:42.26,000 --> 0:11:45,000
where the feed is being produced and being transported.

289
0:11:45.26,000 --> 0:11:47,000
We can increase it a bit

290
0:11:47.26,000 --> 0:11:49,000
at the expense of rainforests,

291
0:11:49.26,000 --> 0:11:51,000
but there's a limitation very soon.

292
0:11:51.26,000 --> 0:11:53,000
And if you remember that we need to increase

293
0:11:53.26,000 --> 0:11:55,000
agricultural production by 70 percent,

294
0:11:55.26,000 --> 0:11:57,000
we're not going to make it that way.

295
0:11:57.26,000 --> 0:11:59,000
We could much better change

296
0:11:59.26,000 --> 0:12:02,000
from meat, from beef,

297
0:12:02.26,000 --> 0:12:04,000
to insects.

298
0:12:04.26,000 --> 0:12:07,000
And then 80 percent of the world

299
0:12:07.26,000 --> 0:12:09,000
already eats insects,

300
0:12:09.26,000 --> 0:12:11,000
so we are just a minority --

301
0:12:11.26,000 --> 0:12:14,000
in a country like the U.K., the USA,

302
0:12:14.26,000 --> 0:12:17,000
the Netherlands, anywhere.

