308
0:12:31.26,000 --> 0:12:33,000
not because they're hungry,

309
0:12:33.26,000 --> 0:12:35,000
but because they think it's a delicacy.

310
0:12:35.26,000 --> 0:12:37,000
It's just very good food.

311
0:12:37.26,000 --> 0:12:39,000
You can vary enormously.

312
0:12:39.26,000 --> 0:12:41,000
It has many benefits.

313
0:12:41.26,000 --> 0:12:43,000
In fact, we have delicacy

314
0:12:43.26,000 --> 0:12:45,000
that's very much like this grasshopper:

