322
0:13:00.26,000 --> 0:13:02,000
They are delicacies.

323
0:13:02.26,000 --> 0:13:05,000
In fact, a locust is a "shrimp" of the land,

324
0:13:05.26,000 --> 0:13:08,000
and it would make very good into our diet.

325
0:13:08.26,000 --> 0:13:1,000
So why are we not eating insects yet?

326
0:13:10.26,000 --> 0:13:12,000
