328
0:13:14.26,000 --> 0:13:17,000
and we see insects as these organisms that are very different from us.

329
0:13:17.26,000 --> 0:13:2,000
That's why we're changing the perception of insects.

330
0:13:20.26,000 --> 0:13:23,000
